data.description: RANGE PRICING Seller will accept or counter offers between $359,990-$369,990.  ASSUMABLE VA LOAN at 2.875% INTEREST!!! You must see this home. Ample windows bathe the space in natural light, easy care scored concrete floors create an inviting and warm ambiance. At the heart of this home, the gourmet kitchen draws you in with a spacious granite wrap-around breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, and an abundance of cabinetry w/ soft under cabinet lighting . Seamlessly connected to the living and dining areas, it sets the scene for comfortable day to day living and effortless entertaining. Upstairs you'll find an office nook, spacious bedrooms and a generous master suite w/ walk-in closet.  One of the largest lots in the community, the backyard is a private oasis... ...boasting breathtaking mountain views, stylish pavers, a fire pit and full length patio for gatherings.Located in the desirable Vail School District with top-rated K-8 school right within walking distance! New commercial center with shopping, grocery and restaurants is just minutes away. This is "the one"...Don't miss the chance to make it yours!
